      "content": "It's never going to get easier, but maybe you can find a way to make it bearable. Sometimes, it's about finding the right people who understand, or maybe even finding a way to make yourself understood. But if that's not possible, then maybe it's time to consider other options. Sometimes, the best way to find peace is to stop trying so hard to fit in. It's okay to be alone, and it's okay to not fit in. It's okay to just be you.",
